ENTRY       EC 2.4.1.323                Enzyme
NAME        7-deoxyloganetic acid glucosyltransferase;
            UGT8
CLASS       Transferases;
            Glycosyltransferases;
            Hexosyltransferases
SYSNAME     UDP-alpha-D-glucose:7-deoxyloganetate O-D-glucosyltransferase
REACTION    UDP-alpha-D-glucose + 7-deoxyloganetate = UDP + 7-deoxyloganate
SUBSTRATE   UDP-alpha-D-glucose [CPD:C00029];
            7-deoxyloganetate
PRODUCT     UDP [CPD:C00015];
            7-deoxyloganate [CPD:C11636]
COMMENT     Isolated from the plant Catharanthus roseus (Madagascar periwinkle). Involved in loganin and secologanin biosynthesis. Does not react with 7-deoxyloganetin. cf. EC 2.4.1.324 7-deoxyloganetin glucosyltransferase.
